# Codryn portfolio — project intelligence

- Content edits live in `src/data/` (company, projects, services); avoid hardcoding copy in components.
- Accent color is electric blue `#2B7FFF` aligned with logo center element.
- Contact form uses mailto; swap handler in ContactForm.jsx for Formspree/API when needed.
- Plan/Act workflow: stay in PLAN until user types ACT.
- Logo asset: `public/logo.png`.
